79	// ── Module-singletons ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
80	// The OracleAIClient is constructed once per worker process with the three
81	// direct provider adapters (R-providers). Per DECISIONS.md D6 these talk to
82	// Anthropic, Vertex, and OpenAI APIs directly via @anthropic-ai/sdk,
